<div class="subhead" style="padding-top:3px; padding-bottom:7px">Behind the Scenes at CES</div>
<span class="text">
Check out <EM>Behind the Scenes at CES </EM>for updates on the extra efforts the International CES makes to improve the show and make your experience better. <BR><A name=scene1></A> 
<P><STRONG>Hotel Discounts Now Available!<BR></STRONG>If you’ve got a big staff to house in Vegas for CES—or you just want some discounted hotel rooms—we’re here to help! </P>
<P>The International CES works closely with a variety of properties in Las Vegas to provide you with diverse options for accommodations and deep discounts during your show stay. </P>
<P>Whether you need a room block or a single room, you can make your <A href="/print/attendees/travel/hotel.asp">hotel reservations online</A>. You’ll even get a real time confirmation. </P>Plus, you can avoid the expense of taking a cab. The International CES provides free shuttle bus service between hotels and official show venues.
</span>
