<div class="subhead" style="padding-top:3px; padding-bottom:7px">2005 International CES Exhibitor Workshop</div>
<span class="text">
Save the date, book your room, and get ready to attend this <A href="/print/exhibitors/resource_center/workshop/default.asp">FREE workshop</A> for International CES exhibitors! 
<P>On Tuesday, September 21, 2004 plan to attend the 2005 International CES Exhibitor Workshop in Las Vegas. The workshop will feature informative, one-on-one discussions with International CES representatives, vendors and other exhibitors. Learn how to make your exhibit a success—and get ready to receive vendor discounts. Topics will include Marketing/PR and Operations updates and sessions on freight, utilities, <EM>How to Increase ROI, Learn from the Experts</EM> (an exhibitor panel) and more. </P>We also have discounted rooms waiting for you. The Las Vegas Hilton is offering hotel accommodations for the CES Exhibitor Workshop at $59.00 per night. Make your reservations now. Contact the Hilton directly at (800) 732-7117 or (702) 732-5301, and ask for the 2005 CES Exhibitor Workshop or group SVCEW4.
</span>
<a name="925"></a>
<img src="/print/global_images2005/spacer.gif" alt="" width="100%" height="30" hspace="0" vspace="0" border="0"><br>

