<div class="subhead" style="padding-top:3px; padding-bottom:7px">NY Pre-show Press Event</div>
<span class="text">
Get ready for some face time with 150 of the biggest names in technology media on Wednesday, November 10, 2004 in New York City. These are the tech-savvy gadget gurus you want to be writing about your products. 
<P>It’s a captive audience. This year’s press preview will feature an exhibitor-only executive luncheon, and a press reception, as well as the anticipated announcement of our Innovations 2005 Honorees. So, grab the attention of influential press and analysts before the show starts. Network with key press and media representatives at the Press Preview Reception, and whet their appetite for what you’re bringing to Vegas in January. </P><STRONG>NEW!</STRONG> If you really want to make your mark, <A href="/print/exhibitors/promotions/press.asp">consider sponsoring</A> a suite, kiosk—or both! Not only will you get great publicity, but you’ll be able to include your company name and logo in the press kit materials. For more information, contact Wendy Hudak, Manager, Promotional Opportunities, CES at (703) 907-7688 or <A href="mailto:byb@ce.org">byb@ce.org</A>.
</span>
