<div class="subhead" style="padding-top:3px; padding-bottom:7px">Call for Sponsorship Proposals: Plan Ahead! </div>
<span class="text">
<IMG height=132 hspace=8 src="http://www.cesweb.org/shared_files/edm/2004/exhNews/July/saumsung.jpg" width=200 align=right> You’ve got ‘til Labor Day before you get your “Build Your Brand+ Promotional Opportunities” kit in the mail, but don’t wait! Smart exhibitors are already calling dibs on the most visible opportunities available. 
<P>Will your company name and logo wrap a building and be seen by the 130,000+ attendees at the International CES? Or will your name be all over the popular beaming stations?</P>
<P>Submit your proposal now. Don’t wait until there’s no money left in your budget—or the most popular opportunities are sold out. We’ll help you determine which opportunities are best for the audience you’re trying to target—and stay within your budget. </P>To get your name on the hottest opportunities, contact Wendy Hudak, Manager, Promotional Opportunities, CES at (703) 907-7688 or <A href="mailto:byb@ce.org">byb@ce.org</A>.
</span>
